        <h3> Progress, Levels and Tiers </h3><br>
        The progress bar automatically earns progress. Once it is full, it will empty and both a level and a tier will be earned.
        Progress can be speeded up for some time by clicking the click button. 
        Levels can be spent on 5 level upgrades that increase the progress earned.
        </FlexBox><FlexBox Stretch="true" class="colorflex">

        <h3>Reset</h3> <br>
        Several things can be reset (Levels, level upgrades, etc.) to increase the reset multi, which increases the progress earned.
        After clicking the reset button, there will be further explanation.
        </FlexBox><FlexBox Stretch="true" class="colorflex">

